cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.NE, cs.AI, cs.SI 

The paper deals with multitask learning and feature selection, which are common topics in machine learning (cs.LG) and computer vision (cs.CV). The specific application of the method to fMRI analysis suggests a possible fit with neural engineering (cs.NE) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The use of convex optimization and error bounds may also suggest a connection to optimization and control (cs.SI).
